PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Energy, Mines and Resources of Ralph Lean, of Richmond Hill, Ontario, as a director of the Atomic Energy of Canada Limited to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective May 25, 1993, in the place of Peter Harold Harris, whose term has expired.
